nodes.text: Ooo-temiuk was a forested planet located in a star system on the Triellus Trade Route between C-Foroon and Tatooine in the Arkanis sector of the Outer Rim Territories region of the galaxy. It was colonized around 75 BBY by Rodian migrants fleeing their troubled homeworld. Greel Wood Logging Corporation later established a harvesting facility on the planet.
